 Che5-kok u7 chit8 e5 chhut-mia5 e5 thak8-chheh lang5, mia5 kio3 Chhan5 Tiong7. I m7-ai3 choe3 koaN, kam-goan7 un2-ku san-lim5, choe3 kang tou7 pa2, khoaN3-phoa3 se3-kan beng5-li7 chit nng7 ji7. Au7-lai5 u7 chit8 e5 Song3-kok e5 lang5, mia5 kio3 Khut Kok, lai5 kiN3 i, ka7 i kong2, Goa2 ku2-ku2 chiu7 thiaN-kiN3 sian-siN li2 e5 ho2 mia5-siaN, kong2 li2 peng5-seng koat-toan3 m7 kheng2 kho3 lang5 chiah8 png7. TaN goa2 u7 chit8 khoan2 chai pu5-a2 e5 hoat-tou7 beh hian3 hou7 li2, oe7 hou7 sou2 chai e5 pu5-a2 teng7 khok-khok, na2 chhin-chhiuN7 chioh8-thau5 e5 khoan2, koh chin kau7, ia7 bo5 khang bo5 phang7. Chhan5 Tiong7 thiaN-liau2 chiu7 kong2, Chai pu5-a2 e5 lou7-eng7, si7 beh chiong i lai5 toe2 tang toe2 sai. Na7 si7 teng7 kau3 chhin-chhiuN7 chioh8-thau5, kau7-kau7 koh bo5 khang bo5 phang7, an2-ni chiu7 boe7 eng7 tit thang phoa3-khui khi2-lai5 toe2 mih8 tit. Che beh kap lang5 sng3 choe3 sim2-mih8 pu5-a2 leh? Khut Kok chiu7 in3 i kong2, Na7 an2-ni goa2 chiu7 beh chiong chit e5 hoat-tou7 pang3 hiat kak8 liau2. Chong2-si7 chhin-chhiuN7 Sian-siN chit khoan2 e5 m7 kheng2 kho3 lang5 chiah8 png7, tek-khak ia7 si7 bo5 li7-ek ti7 lang5; kiaN-liau2 sian-siN ia7 si7 kap chit khoan2 teng7 khok-khok e5 pu5-a2 sio siang7 leh. 
 Lang5 kap khim5-siu3 hit e5 toa7 hun-piat e5 sou2-chai7, chiu7-si7 lang5 oe7 chai-kio3 hok8-sai7 Siong7-te3 kap hok8-sai7 lang5. Na7 kan-ta chai u7 i ka-ki7, ia7 long2 m7 chai u7 pat8 lang5, koh m7 chai thang kong2 u7 chit8 ui7 chin-sit8 bo5 lam7-sam2 eng2-oan2 oah8 ti7-teh e5 Chu2-chaiN2, an2-ni chiu7 sit-loh8 choe3 lang5 e5 chu-keh. Sou2-i2 Seng3-keng u7 kong2, Lin2 e5 kng tioh8 chio3 ti7 lang5 e5 bin7-cheng5, hou7 in khoaN3-kiN3 lin2 e5 ho2 sou2 kiaN5, lai5 kui eng5-kng hou7 lin2 ti7 thiN-nih8 e5 Pe7. Chiau3 an2-ni khoaN3 lang5 na7 chhin-chhiuN7 hit ho7 siu-to7-jin5 khi3 un2-ku san-lim5, kan-ta beh kiu3 ka-ki7 e5 leng5-hun5, kiam2 m7 si7 sit-loh8 choe3 lang5 e5 pun2-hun7? 
 Kou3-chip put-thong 
 Teng7-kok u7 chit8 e5 lang5 beh chhut khi3 boe2 chit8 siang oe5, tai7-seng ti7 in chhu3-nih8, chiu7 chiong i e5 kha, niu5 khoaN3 joa7 tng5 joa7 toa7, pi2-kau3 chit8 e5 iuN7 chham kha-nih8 ho5-ho5, chiu7 chhiaN2 he7 ti7 toh-teng2. Au7-lai5 khi3 kau3 ti7 koe-nih8, chiah siuN7-tioh8 boe7 ki3-tit theh8 hit e5 pan7 lai5. Ti7 koe-chhi7 nih8 sui-jian5 u7 chin choe7 e5 oe5, khiok m7-kheng2 boe2, kong2 i boe7 ki3-tit theh8 hit e5 iuN7 lai5 pi2 khoaN3-bai7-teh. Kau3 theng3-hau7 i to3-khi3 in chhu3, theh8 hit e5 iuN7 lai5 e5 si5, to i2-keng soaN3 chhi7, tiam3 long2 koaiN liau2-liau2 lah. In-ui7 an2-ni soa3 boe2 bo5 oe5. U7 lang5 ka7 i kong2, Li2 thai3 m7 eng7 li2 e5 kha loh8-khi3 pi2, chheng7 kau3 oe7 ho5-ho5 tu2 ho2 mih-sai2 tioh8 koh to3-khi3 theh8 hit e5 pan7. I chiu7 in3 kong2, Leng5-khou2 tioh8 sin3 hit e5 pan7, m7-thang sin3 chit siang kha. 
 Na7 lun7 se3-kan, ia7 u7 chit khoan2 hit ho7 lang5, choan-choan si7 sin3 kou2-cha2 e5 hoat-tou7, m7 sin3 sin e5 hoat-tou7, m7 chai kau3 kou2-cha2 e5 hoat-tou7, long2 si7 hah8 ti7 hit e5 si5-ki teh eng7. Na7 si7 kan-ta chai hit e5 kou2-cha2 e5 hoat-tou7, ia7 long2 boe7 hiau2-tit i5-si5 che3-gi5, an2-ni chiu7 tek-khak oe7 gou7 toa7-su7. 
 Oh8 m7 tioh8 iuN7 
 Teng7-koaiN7 e5 sou2-chai7, u7 chit8 e5 lang5 kah in bou2 ka7 i choe3 chit8 nia2 khou3. In bou2 mng7 i kong2, Beh choe3 sim2-mih8 khoan2? Hit e5 lang5 kong2, Chiau3 chhin-chhiuN7 goa2 ku7 e5 khou3 hit khoan2. In bou2 chiu7 chiong hit te3 sin e5 pou3, hui2-hoai7 hou7 phaiN2, chiah choe3 chit8 nia2 kap i e5 ku7 e5 saN-tang5. 
 Koh u7 chit8 hang7; ti7 kui2-chap8 ni5 cheng5, Hiong-kang2 taN-chiah koah kui Eng-kok, chiu7 u7 chin choe7 Eng-kok lang5 lai5 tiam3 ti7 hia, kaN2 si7 in-ui7 iau2-be7 u7 choe3 chhai5-hong5 e5 sai-hu7 lai5, sou2-i2 hiah-e5 Eng-kok lang5, u7 khi3 chhiaN3 hia e5 pun2-toe7 lang5 ka7 in choe3 iuN5-hok8. Hia e5 pun2-toe7 chhai5-hong5 pou7-pin5 m7-bat khoaN3-kiN3 hit khoan2 e5 saN-a2-khou3, khoaN3-liau2 hoan ki3-ka3, chia ia7 chit8 e5 te7-a2, hia ia7 chit8 e5 te7-a2, kui nia2 ui kau3 choan khang. Chiu7 koh mng7 in kong2, Beh chaiN2-iuN7 choe3? Hit e5 Eng-kok lang5 kong2, Chiau3 goa2 ku7 e5 hit khoan2 an2-ni choe3. Hit e5 chhai5-hong5 chiu7 chiau3 in ku7 e5 pan7, ka7 i ka loh8 khi3 choe3, lian5 hit ho7 kiN phoa3 khang koh thiN7 e5, i ia7 chiau3 hit e5 kiN phoa3 e5 se3-bin7, ka7 i ka hou7 khui, chiah koh thiN7. Kau3 au7-lai5 choe3 ho2, hiahN khi3 hou7 hit e5 Eng-kok lang5, thi2-khui khi2-lai5 chit8-e7 khoaN3, thai3 oe7 kui nia2 ka kau3 chia ia7 chit8 khang, hia ia7 chit8 khang, chiah koh pou2 kau3 hoe lok8-lok8? Chiu7 ham i khau-chhau2, m7-na7 m7 kang-chiN5 hou7 i, tian-to3 beh ka7 i tho2 pou3-sin e5 gun5. Liong2-peng5 cheng-lun7 boe7 soah; au7-lai5 u7 lang5 chhut-lai5 ka7 in chhu2, chiah tiau5-tit8. 
 Lun7-kau3 tak8 kok e5 hoat-tou7 kap hong-siok8, to long2 u7 ho2 ia7 u7 phaiN2; m7-ku2 beh than3 hit e5 ho2 e5 khah oh, beh oh8 phaiN2 e5 si7 khah khoai3. Na7 beh kan-ta chai hit-e5 phaiN2 e5 sou2-chai7, ia7 m7 chai thang oh8 ho2 e5, an2-ni kap hit e5 Teng7-kok e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 teh choe3 khou3, chham hit e5 Hiong-kang2 chhai5-hong5 e5 teh choe3 iuN5-hok8, u7 sim2-mih8 koh-iuN7 leh? 
 Sia3-seng chhu2-gi7 
 Tong-iong5 Tiong5-pan2-pho Tio7 Chu2-liong5 kiu3 A-tau2, hit-si5 Lau5 Pi7 kap Cho5 Chho3 kau-chian3, Lau5 Pi7 thai5-su, i e5 chiong3 kap ke-koan3 long2 si3-soaN3 liau2-liau2. I u7 chit8-e5 tai7-chiong3 mia5 kio3 Tio7 Chu2-liong5, ti7 pah-ban7 kun-tiong beh chhe7 in e5 chu2-bu2 kap sio2 chu2-lang5, jip8 kau3 Tiong5-pan2-pho e5 lam5-peng5, chiah khoaN3-kiN3 hu-jin5 pho7 A-tau2 ti7 chit8 e5 phoa3 chhiuN5-a2 e7 chiN2-noa5-teng2 teh che7, bak8-sai2 si3-lam5-sui5. Chu2-liong5 siuN7-khi2 Lau5 Pi7 tok8-tok8 chit e5 kiaN2 na7-tiaN7, na7 bo5 kiu3 i chiu7 Han3-tiau5 soa3 choat8-su5, chiu7 koaN2-kin2 chhiaN2 Bi2 Hu-jin5 chiuN7 be2, thang saN-kap to5-mia7. Hu-jin5 kong2, Goa2 si2 si7 bo5 iau3-kin2, chong2-si7 in lau7-pe7 chi2-u7 chit8 e5 kiaN2 na7-tiaN7, choan-choan oa2-kho3 chiong-kun po2-hou7 i, m7-thang in-ui7 goa2 lai5 lian5-lui7 li2. Kong2-liau2 chiu7 chiong A-tau2 pho7 hou7 i, soa3 thiau3 loh8 kou2-chiN2--nih8 si2. Chu2-liong5 chiu7 chiong A-tau2 pak8 toa3 seng-khu--nih8 phe siN3-mia7 phah chhut ban7-teng5-ui5, chiong A-tau2 lai5 heng5 Lau5 Pi7. Au7-lai5 ti7 Se-siok8 chiap-ui7 choe3 hong5-te3. Che sit8-chai7 si7 choan kho3 Chu2-liong5 e5 iong2-beng2. 
 Lan2 thak8 chit khoan2 e5 kou2-tian2, siuN7 khi2 Bi2 Hu-jin5 pang3-sak siN3-mia7, Chu2-liong5 phe-mia7 kau-chian3, an2-ni lai5 kiu3 A-tau2, si7 in-ui7 A-tau2 e5 si2 oah8 chiu7-si7 koan-he7 Han3-tiau5 e5 chun5 bong5, sou2-i2 khoaN3 choe3 bo5 ke3 e5 po2-poe3; pang3-sak siN3-mia7 lai5 kiu3 i, chiau3 li2-khi3 khiok eng-kai tioh8 an2-ni. 
 TaN se3-kan lang5 sou2 po2-poe3--e5 chiu7-si7 siN3-mia7, na7-si7 iau2 u7 pi2 siN3-mia7 koh khah iau3-kin2 e5, chiu7-si7 boe7 si2-sit, boe7 biat8-bo5 e5 leng5-hun5. Ki-tok kang3-lim5 lai5 se3-kan, pang3-sak siN3-mia7 ti7 sip8-ji7-ke3, che tiau5-kou3-i3 si7 beh lai5 kiu3 se3-kan lang5 e5 leng5-hun5. Seng3-keng u7 kong2, Jin5-chu2 kau3, si7 beh kiu3 sit-loh8 e5 lang5 (Thai3 18: 11). 
 Kui2-koai3 e5 pun2-su7 
 Chai7-cha2 u7 chit8 e5 lang5 teh ka7 Che5-ong5 ui7 ji7-ui7, Che5-ong5 mng7 i kong2, Ui7 sim2-mih8 te7-it ui5-lan5? Hit e5 ui7-kang kong2, Kau2 be2 choe3 ui5-lan5. Che5-ong5 koh mng7 kong2, Ui7 sim2-mih8 te7 it khoai3? Ui7-kang koh in3 i kong2, Kui2-koai3 iau-chiN choe3 khoai3 ui7. In-ui7 kau2 be2 si7 lang5 cha2-am3 siong5-siong5 teh khoaN3, na7 ui7 chit8-tiam2-a2 bo5 tu2-ho2 hah8, lang5 chiu7 liam5-piN khoaN3 oe7 chhut; sou2-i2 khah oh-tit ui7. Iau-chiN kui2-koai3 sng3-si7 bo5 heng5 bo5 iaN2, ia7 bo5 lang5 bat khoaN3-kiN3; put-lun7 ui7 sim2-mih8 khoan2, lang5 long2 boe7 hiau2-tit hun-piat, sou2-i2 u7 khoai3 ui7. 
 Se3-kan eng2 u7 chit cheng2 lang5, chin gau5 chng-ki5 choe3-koai3, piN3 hiah-e5 ki5-koai3 e5 tai7-chi3, ka-ki7 liah8 choe3 si7 chin gau5, ki5-sit8 long2 si7 hiah-e5 ui7 kui2-koai3 e5 pun2-su7, lai5 teh phian3 lang5 na7-tiaN7. Che ia7 thang pi2-pheng7 chhin-chhiuN7 lang5 kong2 in u7 hoat-tou7 thang phoa3 te7-gek8 khui thian-tong5, che khiok khah khoai3 kong2, in-ui7 oh-tit thang kap in pian7-pok. Chong2-si7 lang5 na7 kong2 in u7 hoat-tou7 thang kiu3 lang5 chhut in e5 phaiN2, piN3 choe3 ho2 lang5, che khah oh-tit kong2, in-ui7 u7 iaN2 bo5 iaN2 lang5 liam5-piN chai. Ia7 chhin-chhiuN7 Ma2-kho2 2: 9 sou2 ki3-chai3 Ia5-sou mng7 cheng3 lang5 kong2, Ka7 pian3-sui7 e5 kong2, Li2 e5 choe7 sia3 lah, a2-si7 kong2, Khi2-lai5, gia5 li2 e5 phou-a2 lai5 kiaN5, toh-loh8 chit8 hang7 khah khoai3? Chiu7 tng cheng3 lang5 e5 bin7-cheng5 i-ho2 hit e5 lang5, hou7 lang5 chai Jin5-chu2 ti7 toe7--nih8 u7 koan5 thang sia3 choe7. Lan2 e5 Seng3-kau3 na7 u7 kong-hau7 thang kiu3 phaiN2 lang5 piN3 choe3 ho2 lang5, hou7 lang5 khoaN3, peh-siN3 chiu7 khah khoai3 sin3 lan2 sou2 kong2 boe7 khoaN3-kiN3 e5 su7. 
 Bat lang5 khah-ho2 bat chiN5 
 Lou2-kok e5 chaiN2-siang3 Beng7 Hian3-chu2, khi3 Chin3-kok tiau5-pheng3. Chin3-kok e5 chaiN2-siong3, Han5 Soan-chu2, siat ian5-siah8 khoan2-thai7 i; oaN7 saN-ui7 e5 kheh thiaN, long2 pai5 kau3 chin sui2, chin chiau5-pi7, koh chin ho2 khoaN3. Hian3-chu2 kong2, Chin-chiaN3 si7 pu3 kau3-kek8 liau2. Soan-chu2 kong2, Lin2 chhu3 pi2 goan2 chia an2-chaiN2-iuN7? Hian3-chu2 kong2, Goan2 chhu3 song3 kau3 m7 ho2 kong2. Chi2-u7 nng7 e5 thak8-chheh lang5, chit8-e5 mia5 kio3 Gan5 Hoe5, chit8-e5 mia5 kio3 Chu Bu5-leng5, hou7 goa2 tit-tioh8 kok--nih8 oe7 peng5-tiaN7, peh-siN3 oe7 an-un2; goa2 sou2 u7 e5, chin7 chai7 an2-ni na7-tiaN7. Kau3 Hian3-chu2 chhut-khi3, Soan-chu2 chiah kong2, I si7 kun-chu2 e5 lang5, liah8 hit ho7 poe5-iuN2 gau5-lang5 choe3 ho2-giah8. Goa2 si7 siau2-jin5 e5 lang5, chiah liah8 chiah-e5 kim-gun5 chu-gek8 choe3 ho2-giah8. Goa2 ka-ki7 siuN7 sit8-chai7 chin kian3-siau3. 
 Siok8-gu2 kong2, Bat lang5 khah ho2 bat chiN5, sit8-chai7 chin u7-iaN2. M7-ku2 se3-kan lang5, m7-tan7-na7 peng5-iu2, in-ui7 chiN5-chai5 lai5 choat8-kau, chiu7-si7 hiaN-ti7, pe7-bu2, bou2-kiaN2, i2-kip8 chhin-chhek e5 teh kau-chiap, to tioh8 chit hang7 chiN5 choe3 thau5-cheng5. An2-ni kho2-kian3 chiN5 e5 khui3-lat8 si7 chin toa7, chin gau5 pe2-pak8 lang5, na7 m7 si7 hit ho7 kam-goan7 hou7 i song3-hiong hoaN-hi2 khoai3-lok8 lai5 siu2 to7-li2 e5 lang5, chiu7 bo5 hiah khoai3 oe7 thoat-li7 chit hang7 e5 pe2-pak8. Ma2-kho2 10: 23, Ia5-sou tui3 I e5 hak8-seng kong2, Pu3 lang5 beh jip8 Siong7-te3 e5 kok si7 chin oh. Che si7 in-ui7 u7 chit8 e5 ho2-giah8 lang5 lai5 kiN3 Ia5-sou, kui7-teh kiu5 khoaN3 tioh8 chaiN2-iuN7 choe3, chiah oe7 tit-tioh8 eng2-oan2 oah8. Ia5-sou kio3 i tioh8 khi3 pian3 boe7 i e5 ke-giap8, lai5 chin2-che3 song3-hiong lang5, chiu7 chiN5-chai5 chek-chu7 ti7 thiN-nih8; chong2-si7 hit e5 lang5 thiaN-kiN3 chit ho7 oe7, bin7 sui5-si5 pian3-sek, u7 iu-chhiu5 e5 khoan2, ia7 soa3 choe3 i khi3. An2-ni kho2-kian3 chiN5-chai5 e5 khui3-lat8 teh pak8 lang5 si7 chin toa7. Ai3 tit thoat-li7 chit khoan2 e5 pe2-pak8, tek-khak tioh8 khoaN3 oe7 phoa3 chiah-e5 se3-kan e5 eng5-hian2; m7-thang chhin-chhiuN7 Han5 Soan-chu2, kan-ta oe7 hiau2-tit chng-thaN7 goa7-bin7 e5 ho2 khoaN3. 
 Chai7 Chin5 ui7 Chin5 
 Han3-tiau5 e5 si5 u7 chit8 e5 lang5 mia5 kio3 Koai2 Thong, si7 choe3 Han5 Sin3 e5 chham-bou5. Kau3 Han5 Sin3 khi3 phoa3 Che5-kok liau2-au7, Koai2 Thong u7 kio3 Han5 Sin3 tioh8 poan7 Han3, chiong Che5-kok tok8-lip8 khi2-lai5 koan2. Han5 Sin3 put-jim2 ki5 sim, m7 thiaN i e5 chhui3. Au7-lai5 Han5 Sin3 hou7 Han3 Ko-chou2 thai5-khi3. Koai2 Thong ia7 hou7 liah8 lai5. Han3 Ko-chou2 mng7 i kong2, Li2 bat kah Han5 Sin3 cho7 hoan2 mah? Koai2 Thong in3 i kong2, To7-chek (kou2-cha2 e5 phaiN2 lang5)e5 kau2, khoaN3-kiN3 Giau5-te3 (kou2-cha2 e5 seng3-ong5)chiu7 toa7 pui7, chong2-si7 Giau5-te3 m7-si7 put-jin5 e5 jin5-kun, kau2 khoaN3-kiN3 m7 si7 i e5 chu2-lang5, khiok si7 boe7 bian2-tit bo5 pui7. Tong-si5 goa2 chai-kio3 u7 Han5 Sin3, khiok boe7 hiau2-tit u7 Pe3-ha7. Han3 Ko-chou2 thiaN-liau2 soa3 sia3-bian2 i e5 choe7. 
 Lang5 kong2, Chai7 Chin5 ui7 Chin5, chai7 Chhou2 ui7 Chhou2, sng3 si7 kah lang5 tioh8 chin7-tiong, tioh8 chin7 pun2-hun7. Chong2-si7 ia7 ai3 khoaN3 si7 sim2-mih8 khoan2 e5 chin7-tiong. U7 chit8 cheng2 hit ho7 pai7-ka chu2-te7, chham hiah-e5 Ong5--ko Liu2--ko khi3 oang, long2 bo5 beh kou3 lai7-thau5, sim7-chi3 tau3 hiah-e5 lai5 khi-hu7 in e5 chhin hiaN-ti7. Ia7 u7 chit8-chiong2 hit-ho7 choan-bun5 teh pang-chan7 tui3-tek8, lai5 siong-hai7 pun2-sin e5 bu2-kok, i ia7 hia-hia pai-pai, ka-ki7 kong2 si7 cheng3-tit8 bo5 phian-su, si7 chin7-tiong teh po3 kok, m7 chai an2-ni tui3 sim2-mih8 lang5 teh chin7-tiong, ia7 teh po3 sim2-mih8 lang5 e5 kok. Hai3-ah! Chhin-chhiuN7 chit khoan2 e5 chin7-tiong, chit khoan2 e5 sim-koaN, soa3 khah-su hit ho7 kau2 e5 lui7, ia7 soa3 m7 chai thang hun-piat ho2 phaiN2. 
 PoaN chhu3 boe7 ki3-tit poaN bou2 
 Lou2 Ai-kong mng7 Khong2-chu2 kong2, Goa2 thiaN-kiN3 lang5 teh kong2, hit ho7 chin gau5 boe7 ki3-tit tai7-chi3 e5 lang5, teh poaN chhu3 e5 si5, lian5 in bou2 ia7 boe7 ki3-tit poaN khi3. Khong2-chu2 kong2, Che iau2 m7 si7 gau5 boe7 ki3-tit e5 lang5; hit ho7 chin gau5 boe7 ki3-tit e5 lang5, lian5 i pun2-sin ia7 soa3 boe7 ki3-tit. Ai-kong mng7 kong2, An3-chaiN2-iuN7 pun2-sin ia7 soa3 boe7 ki3-tit? Khong2-chu2 kong2, Kou2-cha2 e5 si5 u7 chit8 e5 Ha7 Kiat8-ong5, i e5 chun-kui3 choe3 kau3 hong5-te3, i e5 ho2-giah8 koan2 kau3 thong kok. M7-ku2 m7 than3 sian-ong5 e5 to7-li2, chhia-chhi2 ian3-lok8, be5 ti7 chiu2-sek; au7-lai5 kok phoa3 ka bong5, soa3 hou7 Thong-ong5 thai5-khi3, che kiam2 m7 si7 soa3 boe7 ki3-tit i pun2-sin mah? 
 Se3-kan hit ho7 boe7 ki3-tit pun2-sin e5 lang5, kiam2 kan-ta Ha7 Kiat8 na7-tiaN7? Se3-kan boe7 ki3-tit pun2-sin e5 su7, ia7 m7-tan7-na7 chiu2-sek na7-tiaN7. Hoan7-na7 lang5 choe3 chit8 hang7 bo5 chiau3 li2-khi3 e5 tai7-chi3, a2 si7 kong2 chit8 ku3 bo5 li2 e5 oe7, i2-kip8 chun5 chit8 hang7 bo5 to7-li2 e5 liam7-thau5, chiu7 long2 kau3-giah8 thang hai7-tioh8 in e5 seng-khu kap sim-koaN. Sou2-i2 kou2-cha2 kun-chu2 e5 lang5, tui3 ka-ki7 chit8 e5, ia7 tioh8 chun5 kin2-sin7 keng2-kai3 e5 sim. 
 Bo5 sin3 pin5, oe7 gou7 su7 
